						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar in the compound of Jyōtirliṅga temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 17th century.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Svabhānu, Bhādrapada ba. 30. The details cannot be verified.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of land by [Mādi]dēva-nāyaka of Barige for maintaining a charitable picotta. The inscription is damaged.</p>						

						</summary>
